		"Name": "BattleHammer",
		"Details": "Pafftek Industries, trying to reduce the cost of the exceptional BattleHammer, made a series utilizing only inner-sphere tech.  This BH-3HM BattleHammer variant brings the Hyper-velocity Missile Launcher as its primary armarment.   The HVM has an extreme range that pairs well with the BattleHammer's mobility.  The BH-3HM is meant to deploy as a long-range hole puncher and is not the \"combat at all ranges\" role that the BattleHammer typically occupies.\n\n <b><color=#e51717>COMMUNITY CONTENT</color></b>",
